             sworn. - Mrs. Mary Littlewood is a widow, and keeps a house in the parish of <placeName id="t18021027-50-crimeloc273">Hendon</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18021027-50-crimeloc273" type="placeName" value="Hendon"></interp>
